next thing you know, everything is terribly wrong.

Don’t knowingly put yourself in these situations.
Don’t push the limits if you’re not ready.

Don’t be too trusting of people you don’t know
very well. _

Remember this: Rape is not a crime of passion.
Rape is a crime of violence.

It is possibly the most violent act anybody can
commit. It is certainly the most violent thing anyone
can experience. ‘

